{{DISPLAYTITLE:A_SpectreChunkLarge}}
'''A_SpectreChunkLarge'''<br />
(no parameters)

Spawns a {{Class|AlienChunkLarge|large alien chunk}} ten units above the calling actor's feet, gives it a horizontal velocity between -7 and 8 on both the X and Y axis, and a vertical momentum between 0 and 15.

This codepointer is restricted to {{Class|SpectralMonster}} and derived classes.

[[Category:Decorate Strife functions]] [[Category:Decorate Spawn functions]] [[Category:Decorate Restricted functions]]{{DEFAULTSORT:SpectreChunkLarge}}
